Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:12.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强等人搭乘的万能潜水艇 鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直在追踪石像鬼的飞行船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却反而落入陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遭到水雷包围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到帮助众人脱离险境的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟是强与三人组的活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:49.01,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#11 鹦鹉螺号的新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我反对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们有个远大的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了达成那个目标 我们不惜投入所有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在让来路不明的漂流者 轻易成为我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是会妨碍目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚至还可能会使得 鹦鹉螺号陷入危机之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是目前人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加上我认为 他们昨天应付石像鬼陷阱的表现 值得嘉许
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要他们和石像鬼是敌对关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不算违背我们的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯一让人挂心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害怕他们将鹦鹉螺号的秘密 带回地面上滥用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这点倒是用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前的人们还无法理解 这艘船的科学理论
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船的超科学 就连我们也尚未完全理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算会操作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也无法加以复制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是也不能就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还要被关在 这种狭小的地方多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就算穿上新西装 也没意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你每套不都一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真没眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它们存在着微妙的差异
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才说你这个人真没品味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不说这个了 我们能留在这艘船上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可受不了一直被关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是鹦鹉螺号的科学技术 真的很先进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想请他们教我潜水装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再把它装到葛兰坦上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们怎么可能会轻易教人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话虽如此 我们的命运 还是全得看大姐头的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完美无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝小姐 今天的你变得更美了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌啦 尼莫船长 你真是会说客套话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不 我这个男人从不说客套话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就决定让葛兰迪丝 桑森、韩森等三人担任见习船员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不服吗？艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们三人可以信任吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尤其是葛兰迪丝小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？这艘船的见习船员？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请各位从今天起 在我的指挥下做事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说是你们在说 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是谁提议那么做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神啊 谢谢您实现了我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想学习这艘船的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船的科学非常了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它做到了 至今从未有人做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想学习这艘船的科学 为世上贡献一份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我不能准许你 在船内自由走动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你可以尽情阅读 我房里的书籍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你 艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我该做什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们是这艘船的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以请你与强一样 遵守船内的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 请让我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直以来我都是以劳力 赚取自己的生活所需
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟『没工作的人就没资格吃饭』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 那就麻烦你协助葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉会做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉什么都会做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 我会想想你的工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也要工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,点亮舰内配置图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始进行说明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是鹦鹉螺号的内部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前我们位在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,依序是停机库 居住区 仓库 动力室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么没看到螺旋桨？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船是靠水流喷射推进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水流喷射推进就是先电解 由吸水口吸入的水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再使用超导体线圈 产生电磁感应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由后方喷出等离子体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藉其反作用力使船身前进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将水电解产生电磁感应…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能供给如此强大的 动力源是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该不可能是 一般的蒸气机或电池
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动力源就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本舰的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它是以怎样的装置在运作的？ 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂 我没那么老吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还是哥哥级的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那喷射的动力源呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠我们自豪的成对消灭…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙 不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？你再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们就放我一马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关于这点不方便由我透露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 只要有那个引擎 长嘴硬鳞鱼号根本不是我们的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也见过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是石像鬼的潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来我将特别带你们 参观舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 作战时一律不得进入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 玛莉 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉要工作 不要念书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是玛莉 小孩子的工作就是念书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉才不是小孩子 所以要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是念书就等于是在工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你来跟我学点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备好啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一加一是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 答案是二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会加法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉也会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 那我要问下个问题啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三减二是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王你不必答 这回轮到我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好土的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原本松垮垮的 我就自己剪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然是你的品味 那我也不好多说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们上厨房战场去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷冻柜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷冻柜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的耶 东西都结冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冰是从哪里放进去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这并不是用冰块来冷冻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是靠电力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,电力？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,电力是冰的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是个厨师 不懂那些复杂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那炉子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然也是用电
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烤箱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打果汁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打蛋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,洗碗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烤箱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果汁机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打蛋器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而这是洗碗机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 全都是用电的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,电力真是种方便的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 有两件事无法靠电力完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是切菜的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及让享用料理的人 所感受到的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又切到手了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近的小孩 连海带都切不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 做事那么不灵光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样你就算有再多只手指头 也不够切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你把那个盖子打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对喔 你说过 你不吃鱼也不吃肉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天的伙食就由我一个人负责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老人家跟小ㄚ头到角落休息去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 居然全都是鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样很难变化菜色耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然敢摸那些鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么好怕的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又不会被咬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那些都是尸体耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尸体？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些是料理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还是要做给 我心爱的尼莫先生吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再来就是…爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个…是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这道菜名叫『葛兰迪丝风味』 『疏刺安康爱的呼唤』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那为什么只给我们喝汤跟水？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住口 你还年轻不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快啊 请趁热享用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 不合你的口味吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 虽然卖相不怎么好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但味道挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我来试一口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王的事虽然也令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到葛兰迪丝小姐 还有那样的拿手绝活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能说人不可貌相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关于娜蒂亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 她无论做什么都失败连连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 她都能撑到现在了 我想应该不需要太过担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为至今都没人教导她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也没有人教导过我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,考量了鹦鹉螺号的食材数量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伙食内容就变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都在忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该不会有人想抱怨吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们就开动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能跟尼莫先生吃到同样的菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她说了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她自己吃鱼 我们却只有马铃薯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们怎么了？ 有什么意见是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是觉得这盘马铃薯泥 看起来好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么马铃薯泥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些全都是鱼肉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真没规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胡椒似乎少了点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 韩森 有不满就直接说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不像男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从刚才就一直碎碎念不停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没做事的人 有什么资格要求享受？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是狮子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然敢弄伤少女的玉肌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 你跑哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那里是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 餐才用到一半 他们真没规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一群怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,静电？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们是不能进入舰桥的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别那么死板行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论理由为何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你都必须严格遵守舰内规定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为你老爱说些 不知变通的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看起来才会那么老
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个房间是做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来你跑到这里来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这到底会是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又不是发电机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是本舰的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,常温成对消灭引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成对消灭引擎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问那是什么样的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够让氢原子 与反氢原子成对消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:18:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将其94%的质量转换为能源的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯一一架半永久引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听起来好深奥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十九世纪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 就算是过了二十世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们人类还是创造不出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果用不同的使用方式 甚至能靠它飞越银河
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,登上宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒 这真是人类的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类的宝藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 若是使用者心术不正
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它反而会成为 毁了整个地球的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船目前 也不过是个杀人工具罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 科学确实有其美好之处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够化不可能为可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 科学同时也背负了 吃下智慧果实之人们的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你千万不能忘记这点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你快点让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是禁止进入的引擎室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别那么古板嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是要去找大王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论理由为何 我都不能让你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你跑哪里去了？害我好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后不可以再乱跑了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你就乖乖听话 把蔚蓝之水…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把大王交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追根究底 明明就是你先欺负大王的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,废话少说 把它交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是在吵什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是想跟大王玩玩罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在都已经是科学时代了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我们还得做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要还待在这艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们就注定是这种命运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在碎碎念什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且这都要怪你们没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 尼莫先生 动怒的表情也好帅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想亲吻这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确 好久没见到太阳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我 快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我从不晓得风和阳光 会是这么棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老是抱著书在啃的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:21:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是觉得待在天空之下 比窝在科学精华里来得好是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来的24小时 本船将航行于海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这段时间内 你们可以随时上甲板来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请先别走啊 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我愈想就愈搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 是我能回答的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船是杀人工具吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是尼莫船长说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我原本要去找大王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果却闯进引擎室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 瞒着你没说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了 看在你那么老实的份上 原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,科学背负了 吃下智慧果实之人们的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 这句话是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要人同时拥有善心与恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,科学就同时拥有善与恶两种面相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为是人在运用科学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法完全掌控的强大力量 只会招来更多的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就好比这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法完全掌控的强大力量 只会招来更多的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就好比这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你总有一天会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦 一直发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在想尼莫船长的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船是好的那边 还是坏的那边？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是好的那边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为尼莫船长人那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夜晚的海好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一片漆黑 像是会把人吸进去似的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 人类和这片大海比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能算是很渺小的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更别说是与浩瀚宇宙相比了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:54.78,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:24:02.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:08.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:21.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:31.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.48,0:24:40.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.29,0:24:44.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:49.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.23,0:24:58.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.15,0:25:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们来到无人岛上野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.76,0:25:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我从不晓得踏在土地上 会让人那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.46,0:25:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 因为一直都踏在 鹦鹉螺号的金属地板上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.96,0:25:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你看 好美的贝壳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.53,0:25:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你也很…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.90,0:25:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 葛兰迪丝在叫我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.40,0:25:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『葛兰迪丝的初恋』
